  "display_name": "Cell Image Analysis Techniques",
  "description": "This cluster of papers covers advanced techniques and tools in bioimage analysis, microscopy, and high-content screening. It includes topics such as machine learning for cellular image analysis, automated neuronal morphology reconstruction, deep learning applications, and phenotypic profiling of cellular responses. The papers also discuss the use of advanced image processing methods and the integration of high-throughput microscopy in drug discovery.",
